<h3>Your Profile</h3>

<p>Your Gravatar: <%= image_tag current_user.gravatar_url(:size => 60), :id => 'profile_gravatar' %> (change it at <%= link_to 'gravatar.com', 'http://www.gravatar.com' %>)</p>

<p>Your API key is <strong><%= @user.api_key %></strong>. <br />
   The following line should be added to your <code>~/.gemrc</code> file if isn't there already.</p>

<pre><code>gemcutter_key: <%= @user.api_key %></code></pre>

<p><%= button_to "Reset my API key", reset_api_v1_api_key_path, 
        :method => :put, :confirm => "Are you sure? This cannot be undone." %></p>
